  the ND restriction applies to modification of the textual content
  itself; format conversion and reuse of headword lists are permitted.
  This project extracts only the headword (詞條) and its bopomofo
  reading — no definitions, examples, or other textual content from
  the original dictionary is incorporated.

Legislative Yuan Open Data Platform - 第11屆立法委員姓名
