  Source: https://data.ly.gov.tw/getds.action?id=16
  Location in this repo: data-provider/custom-data/tw-politicians.csv
  Note: This project extracts only legislator names and generates
  bopomofo readings from the local dictionary at build-time. The
  generated file also includes a small QBopomofo-maintained seed list
  of high-profile Taiwan political figures.

